    <!-- Info Page -->
    <string name="about_app">Dog Yarn It is an application designed to provide knitters with a
        simple and reliable way to create custom patterns for their dog sweater projects.\n\n
       All that Dog Yarn It needs to provide you with accurate, form-fitting sweaters is a set of
        measurements of your pet. After that, you can customize the style and yarn type for your
        sweater and get instant feedback.\n\n
       This application was developed for knittingAstor Design Ventures Inc.
    </string>
    <string name="about_astor">Astor Tsang is a Vancouver-based knitwear designer and knitting instructor
        who specializes in pattern design and creation.\n\nDog Yarn It represents Astor\'s desire to provide
        a simple, appealing way for knitters to knit sweaters for dogs of all shapes and sizes.
    </string>

    <string name="about_vicky">Vicky Kim is a Vancouver based illustrator and graphic designer with a
    BFA from Emily Carr University of Art and Design.\n\nShe is currently working as a freelance illustrator,
    collaborating with various companies to create personalized illustrations according to company needs.
    </string>

    <string name="about_team">This app was created by four students from the British Columbia
        Institute of Technology over a 15 week period. These team members are:\n\n\
        Georgi Hristov\n
        Christofer Klassen\n
        Rhea Lauzon\n
        Eric Tsang
    </string>

